title: Windows Key Enterprise v9.0 build 319
description:
Passware Windows Key Enterprise Edition v9.0 Build 319 

Windows Key is an easy-to-use tool to gain access into any Windows 
system if a login password is lost. The software allows you to reset 
passwords in a matter of minutes - no need to reinstall the system. 

Windows Key creates a password reset CD, USB Flash Drive or a driver 
floppy that work during the boot process and instantly reset 
Administrator or other account passwords and Windows security 
settings that prevent you from logging in. 

- Resets Local Administrator password. 

- Resets passwords for other local accounts. 

- Resets Domain Administrator password. 

- Resets local policy settings. 

- Displays account properties. 

- Supports all Service Packs. 

- Supports Windows Vista/XP/2000/NT workstations (including Windows XP 
Tablet PC Edition). 

- Supports Windows 2008/2003/2000/NT servers (including Windows Server 

2003 R2).


[http://www.lostpassword.com/windows-enterprise.htm]
